## Important Reminders

{% for reminder in important_reminders %}
- {{ reminder }}
{% endfor %}

{% if warnings %}
**Warnings**:
{% for warning in warnings %}
- ⚠️  {{ warning }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

